race.comment: BOLT AWAY NOW (2) improved last start but found one better over this trip at Tamworth, beaten one length after being in contention on the bend. Peaking now and can get the job done. LUCKY OZZIE (8) also got off the mark at the latest. Is lightly raced and has plenty of scope for improvement. VISUALISE (5) was doing his best work late when resuming at Armidale. Will appreciate the rise in trip and can play a role in the finish. MR CHIPS (6) was way too good for them last time at Tamworth when shedding his tag. Tougher now but is drawn to advantage and should be in this for a long way.
